        <properties>
          <disabledTextColor color="-16777216"/>
          <editable value="false"/>
          <font name="Berlin Sans FB Demi" size="22"/>
          <lineWrap value="true"/>
          <preferredSize width="1280" height="315"/>
          <text value="This game is a cross between 'Who Wants to be a Millionaire' and 'Mastermind'&#10;For each question, you must choose a category (general knowledge, sport, countries).&#10;You must choose 1 of the 4 possible answers given.&#10;If you answer the question correctly, you will be rewarded with an amount of 'money' based on the difficulty of the question.&#10;The questions get harder as the game progresses.&#10;You have access to 3 types of help facility:&#10;Ask the Public - Displays a rating for each possible answer according to the likelihood that it is the correct answer.&#10;Half-and-half - Two of the possible answers are removed leaving only the correct answer and one incorrect answer.&#10;Give us a Clue - Displays a hint as to which answer is correct.&#10;You may only use each help facility once.&#10;If you choose an incorrect answer, you are out of the game.&#10;The winner is the player with the most money at the end of the game."/>
